	* trans-array.c (get_std_lbound): For derived type variables
	return array valued component lbound.

2011-04-13  Paul Thomas  <pault@gcc.gnu.org>

	PR fortran/48360
	PR fortran/48456
	* gfortran.dg/realloc_on_assign_6.f03: New test.

